ji\" /><br />\n基本上都影響佢純利wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5～7成左右 la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbra brabra~~"},{"pid":"9d495e9017c65f61801e964f8865adc71d77eae7","tid":1117634,"uid":21394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:08:49.000Z","msg":"有咩蛋糕係可以測試間野有冇料到？好似大排擋既乾炒牛河同椒鹽鮮魷。"},{"pid":"8f988bd0c6a922c3c476dd3d27bda22410cd7e7f","tid":1117634,"uid":220220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2bf67f40ef4214c7f0a669ac9286aed8b2640c2b","tid":1117634,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:00:54.000Z","msg":"你覺得邊隻蛋糕最好味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:10:38.000Z","msg":"個人鍾意食芝士蛋糕<br />\n忌廉呀朱古力ar 啲味太濃<br />\n芝士口感係清啲 唔會留係個口咁耐<br />\n反而覺得千層 款式有啲出到厭<br />\n來來去去都係咁 睇唔到出面市場有咩特色出到嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b35d6b657244f09497e010bd3e57cd8760b5948","tid":1117634,"uid":220220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"070a6be077df2e6429a3350b1016ebc4ece2c39d","tid":1117634,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:02:11.000Z","msg":"我冇工返，請唔請人<br />\n利串：咩都唔識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:11:56.000Z","msg":"加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我嗰邊成4個月都冇人見工<br />\n有緣嘅 一定相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016b3389c5a69ff66e1a45c2a4df03659c9cb321","tid":1117634,"uid":220220,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9d495e9017c65f61801e964f8865adc71d77eae7","tid":1117634,"uid":21394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:08:49.000Z","msg":"有咩蛋糕係可以測試間野有冇料到？好似大排擋既乾炒牛河同椒鹽鮮魷。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T21:15:23.000Z",